rows.label: qst660201_msg0001
rows.name: It seems you've had many adventures.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0002
rows.name:
Would you tell me your
stories? I want to put them
to song on this Torigonda.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0003
rows.name:
I'll make it worth your
while, of course.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0102
rows.name:
I'll be sure to make
a fine song of this.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0103
rows.name:
If you have more to tell,
please let me know.

rows.label: qst660201_msg0202
rows.name:
If you change your mind,
please let me know.
